{"tid":1538683,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"田北辰：倘僅撤回修例 未能修補撕裂","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:16:17.000Z","uid":212626,"like":62,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5fa1d3f70b4c1dd6709a102a9ed8f168e00280e5","tid":1538683,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:22.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥下午4時，約見港區人大、政協、建制派立法會議員，到禮賓府會面，預料討論修例風波。有報道指林鄭月娥將會宣布撤回修例。<br />\n<br />\n將出席會面的港區人大代表田北辰表示，若林鄭月娥僅宣布撤回修例，相信不足以修補社會撕裂，建議一併成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，獨立調查委員會成員應由有公信力及無政治傾向的人士出任，相信只要清楚列明調查範圍，不會與監警會重疊職能。檢視範圍包括警方及示威者的行為，如警員是否應展示委任證，以及激進示威者背後是否有培訓及資金等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2241632/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2241632%2F&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=1a10d592\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2241632/</a>"},{"pid":"128c87efc5ca037056d4afb359b089288f1d1424","tid":1538683,"uid":76705,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">黑色炒車警告現正生效<br />\n 切勿跟車太貼</div></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7f4506bb3758c25518be6195f8add88cb275c24f","tid":1538683,"uid":290815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:48.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433c6cd30e67803e7892c01794c55d58e4c2ccb4","tid":1538683,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5767e5915bb3370c497e28a44b0032a7d87a09f0","tid":1538683,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"128c87efc5ca037056d4afb359b089288f1d1424","tid":1538683,"uid":76705,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">黑色炒車警告現正生效<br />\n 切勿跟車太貼</div></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"結果林奠宣佈撤回基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26497882a62df32193ac66ac49f209d11d86e764","tid":1538683,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:38:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民主訴求，缺一不可；<br />\n<br />\n以眼還眼，鷹犬全鎖；<br />\n<br />\n有錯企定，即決勿拖！<br />\n<br />\n民主斬件，仲當我傻！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，未贏收科？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong></span></span></span></span><br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除非你係個班那埋護照旁身嘅扮民霸權，永續利益獨賣囉！！！</span></span></span></span></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"4124ad7fd13cce91e6e8ce8d77fb6087face2642","tid":1538683,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcgb58P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxcgb58P.gif&h=4c045c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ep8qq8P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEp8qq8P.gif&h=b74f62eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">毋忘七烈 千一義 四眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n721元朗 811警暴 831車廂 雙肺 一裙<br />\n無數屈辱私刑 重傷昏迷<br />\n<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</div></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克昏迷、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案</span></strong>事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英、美領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 <br />\n協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐怖 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<strong>人權民主法案 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div>"},{"pid":"6770364a2756fefa31058618ff1eab349e50695e","tid":1538683,"uid":79589,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:39:27.000Z","msg":"唔放入、清算黑警、還我雙普選<br />\n就街頭見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f75aed069d8066dfe3b885f0db384d82c66314f","tid":1538683,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5767e5915bb3370c497e28a44b0032a7d87a09f0","tid":1538683,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"128c87efc5ca037056d4afb359b089288f1d1424","tid":1538683,"uid":76705,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">黑色炒車警告現正生效<br />\n 切勿跟車太貼</div></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"結果林奠宣佈撤回基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3d080e5ff0ae59e54bd9a91a9132f10a721793","tid":1538683,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc6e3fb3d7417e059008d8c505580416798c02e","tid":1538683,"uid":259813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:42:53.000Z","msg":"美帝一出，成班友即刻驚成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歌頌美帝榮耀到永遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOh say can you see"},{"pid":"dbd6472d101a7bb700b63cb519232d9022858893","tid":1538683,"uid":79599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:43:21.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n一，正式撤回逃犯條例<br />\n二，撤回暴動定性<br />\n三，成立獨立調查委員會，追究警察濫權，警黑合作，重組警隊<br />\n四，撤消及釋放由612到現在被捕人士檢控<br />\n五，真普選"},{"pid":"db1ef1181eca64f3120d4cd0db05a5e15db4b4df","tid":1538683,"uid":74155,"l